            <p>
              I have led global teams across 3 continents and helped protect
              revenue streams, platform integrity, and user experiences across
              Cloudflare, Meta, Facebook, PayPal, Qualcomm, and the US Navy.
            </p>
            <p>
              My work sits at the intersection of security engineering,
              operations, product strategy, and cross-functional execution:
              translating complex risk into systems, programs, and teams that
              can move with clarity.
            </p>
            <ul class="skill-list">
              <li>Leadership</li>
              <li>Risk Management</li>
              <li>Technical Program Management</li>
              <li>Product Strategy</li>
              <li>Cloud & Infrastructure Security</li>
              <li>Data & AI Governance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <figure class="portrait-frame">
            <img
              src="/eric-handal-headshot.jpeg"
              alt="Eric Handal"
              width="512"
              height="512"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </figure>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section reveal" id="focus">
