          <span>02 SKILLS</span>
          <div>
            <h2>What I Bring</h2>
            <p>
              Core domains I operate across, from cloud security and data
              governance to product delivery, risk systems, and team leadership.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="focus-grid">
